- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a method for improving neural text-to-speech synthesis using multiple levels of text information.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper focuses on improving the quality of synthesized speech.
- cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing speech signals.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the proposed method involves using pre-training strategies to enhance the model's generalization ability.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a method for improving the performance of a neural TTS system.
